msgctxt "116_Man"
msgid "Hey, aren't you the guy who was givin' our aniki the stink eye?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿no eres el tipo que le estaba mirando feo a nuestro aniki?"

msgctxt "128_Man"
msgid "We'll show you what happens when you fuck with the yakuza!"
msgstr "¡Te vamos a mostrar lo que pasa cuando te metes con la yakuza!"

msgctxt "152_Man"
msgid "We should never have tangled with you..."
msgstr "Nunca debimos habernos metido contigo..."

msgctxt "164_Man"
msgid "This should make up for the trouble..."
msgstr "Esto debería compensar los problemas..."

msgctxt "176_Man"
msgid "You got a tangled %s."
msgstr "Obtuviste un %s."

msgctxt "212_Man"
msgid "We were only following our aniki's orders. It's not like we wanted to beat you up..."
msgstr "Solo estábamos siguiendo las órdenes de nuestro aniki. No es como si quisiéramos golpearte..."

